import React from 'react'
import { Container } from '../Header/styles'
import { Card, Icon, User ,Label, FollowersInfo, Followers, GrowInfo} from './style'
import facebookIcon from '../../images/icon-instagram.svg'
function TopSection() {
    return (
        <Container className = 'container'>
            <Card>
                <User>
                    <Icon src = {facebookIcon}/>

                    <Label>
                        @nathanf
                    </Label>
                </User>
                <FollowersInfo>
                    <Followers>1987</Followers>
                    <Label className= 'followers'>Followers</Label>
                </FollowersInfo>
                <GrowInfo>
                    <Icon></Icon>
                    <Label className ='positive'>12 Today</Label>
                </GrowInfo>
            </Card>
        </Container>
    )
}

export default TopSection
